{"tid":1225693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長輩圖戰線 round 2","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:26:41.000Z","uid":214984,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0bea48b802485c1c1bd16f7f7551ac914c094606","tid":1225693,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:17:50.000Z","msg":"唔好比啲廢老以為暫緩無事！<br />\n第二輪長輩圖同廢老戰線啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n别让林郑跑了！朋友圈都传疯了！<br />\n林郑在习书记明言表态后明白搞垮香港计划泡汤了，打算暂缓执行，等待港英进一步指示。<br />\n内地消息人士指，中央正在想办法处理林郑与英国政府的合作。<br />\n保民生，反修例，坚决维护中央方针，明天一起站出来！不撤回，不撤退！"},{"pid":"3f5cbee354039a37c393dfcf6b17a829ae52ba00","tid":1225693,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a521a95be0c824216ea0197aef54706e307b83a8","tid":1225693,"uid":74954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:26:56.000Z","msg":"[長輩圖]未來目標係打建制派  攻擊議席<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1225711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1225711</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重要指示</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爭奪建制派議席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家援例&nbsp;<br />\n只係令到佢地政府可以平息單野 想爭取番藍絲/中遊支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地有更大既目標就係<span style=\"color: red;\">打散建制派</span>內部支持<br />\n進行<span style=\"color: red;\">內部分化</span>佢地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">選舉就到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫大家出小小idea 方向！￼￼<br />\n<br />\n最衰都係建制派無啦啦轉風，唔全力支持政府，搞到政府咁就跪倒，以後仲點有權威?<br />\n我屋企人都話以後不再選建制派"},{"pid":"a5b0900d6ad4a475e266009a7f0f6a25116ac8d8","tid":1225693,"uid":262065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bea48b802485c1c1bd16f7f7551ac914c094606","tid":1225693,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s